# Welcome to Ambrosia! 

You're seeing this sample content because the /app/gemini directory is empty.

## Quick Start

To add your own content, create .gmi files in the ./gemini directory on your host machine.

## How to Add Your Content

### Option 1: Create files on host
Create a gemini/ folder next to your docker-compose.yml and add .gmi files there.

### Option 2: Copy files into running container
```
docker cp myfile.gmi ambrosia:/app/gemini/
docker restart ambrosia
```

### Option 3: Mount a directory
Update docker-compose.yml to mount your content folder:
```
volumes:
  - /path/to/your/content:/app/gemini:ro
```

